description:
Roasting Ilya, role play, going to Dave Portnoy's house, hardest drug ever taken, working with Tom Ford, and fan Q+A's. Today's guest is our close friend, Jason Nash. Jason is a fellow podcaster, stand up comic, YouTube, and father.


Check out Jason's website here: https://www.thenashnation.com


Check out Jason's Podcast here: https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/all-good-things-with-jason-nash/id1637503076
